<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error - Admin portal</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>body, html {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }
    
    .error-container {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        background-color: #fff;
    }
    
    .error-content {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .error-content h1 {
        font-size: 100px;
        margin: 0;
        color: #ff6b6b;
    }
    
    .error-content h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 10px 0;
        color: #333;
    }
    
    .error-content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #666;
    }
    
    .home-button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #ff6b6b;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .home-button:hover {
        background-color: #ff4b4b;
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-content">
            <h1>Oops!</h1>
            <h2>Something went wrong.</h2>
            <p>We're sorry, but the page you're looking for doesn't exist or an error occurred. Please try again later.</p>
            <a href="/admin/login" class="home-button">Go to Homepage</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
